{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Menjadikan Indiana Jones Karakter Wanita: Ide Buruk atau Sebaliknya? Steven Spielberg Tidak Keberatan!","content":"<p>Sebagai salah satu karya besar sutradara film <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/steven-spielberg-buktikan-dirinya-masih-raja-box-office-dengan-ready-player-one/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Steven ‘<em>Spesialis Box Office</em>’ Spielberg</a> bersama George Lucas, IP dan <em>franchise</em> “Indiana Jones” merupakan serial penting.</p>\n<p>Tidak hanya mengangkat pamor Harrison Ford, yang berperan apik di empat film Indiana Jones sebagai dosen arkeologi petualang, Indiana Jones juga secara tidak langsung merupakan inspirasi konsep “arkeolog petualang jagoan” yang ada di <em>franchise</em> lain seperti <em>video game “Tomb Raider”</em> atau “<em>Uncharted”.</em></p>\n<p><em>Tomb Raider</em> alias Lara Croft dan <em>Uncharted</em> dengan karakter Nathan Drake sedikit banyak terinspirasi dan mengambil elemen-elemen film Steven Spielberg tersebut.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46138\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46138\" data-attachment-id=\"46138\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Ilustrasi Lara Croft, Indiana Jones &#038; Nathan Drake. Sumber: WallDevil\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Ilustrasi Lara Croft, Indiana Jones &#038; Nathan Drake. Sumber: WallDevil&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46138\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian5.jpg\" alt=\"Ilustrasi Lara Croft, Indiana Jones &amp; Nathan Drake. Sumber: WallDevil\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46138\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ilustrasi Lara Croft, Indiana Jones &amp; Nathan Drake. Sumber: WallDevil</p></div></p>\n<p>Hasilnya bagus! Baik<em> Tomb Raider</em> dan <em>Uncharted</em> sukses besar di bisnis <em>video game.</em> <em>Tomb Raider</em> malah juga merambah ke film <em>live action</em> sebanyak 3 kali; dua kali diperankan oleh aktris seksi Angelina Jolie dan sekali oleh aktris muda berbakat Alicia Vikander. Sementara<em> Uncharted</em> masih belum mendapatkan kesempatan untuk beraksi di layar lebar (walau berbagai rumor soal itu bertebaran di internet).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46135\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46135\" data-attachment-id=\"46135\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Dua Lara Croft: Alicia Vikander &#038; Angelina Jolie. Sumber: People\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Dua Lara Croft: Alicia Vikander &#038; Angelina Jolie. Sumber: People&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46135\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian2.jpg\" alt=\"Dua Lara Croft: Alicia Vikander &amp; Angelina Jolie. Sumber: People\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46135\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dua Lara Croft: Alicia Vikander &amp; Angelina Jolie. Sumber: People</p></div></p>\n<p>So… Indiana Jones.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46140\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46140\" data-attachment-id=\"46140\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: SlashFilm\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: SlashFilm&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46140\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian7.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: SlashFilm\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46140\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: SlashFilm</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Franchise</em> ini diciptakan tahun 1981 lewat film perdananya “<em>Indiana Jones and Raiders of the Lost Ark</em>”. Film yang sering dianggap berbagai pihak sebagai salah satu film terbaik yang pernah diciptakan ini, laris luar biasa (dengan modal hanya US$18 Juta dapat menghasilkan lebih dari US$389.9 Juta) serta mendapatkan berbagai pencapaian seperti delapan nominasi Piala Oscar dan memenangi empat di antaranya tahun 1982.</p>\n<p>Pencapaian lainnya adalah film ini disimpan dan dimasukkan ke dalam kategori ‘film nasional’ oleh lembaga pelestarian film Amerika Serikat (<em>U.S. Library of Congress’ National Film Registry</em>). Yang artinya film <em>Raiders of the Lost Ark</em> merupakan bagian penting sejarah nasional perfilman Amerika Serikat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46137\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46137\" data-attachment-id=\"46137\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: GoneWithTheTwins\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: GoneWithTheTwins&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46137\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian4.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: GoneWithTheTwins\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46137\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: GoneWithTheTwins</p></div></p>\n<p>“<em>Indiana Jones</em>” merupakan nama julukan untuk Dr. Henry Walton “Indiana” Jones, Jr. Karakter dengan ciri khas topi fedora, tas model ‘<em>satchel</em>’, jaket kulit dan cambuk ini diperankan oleh aktor legendaris Harrison Ford (di semua film bioskop Indiana Jones yang berjumlah empat film).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46139\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46139\" data-attachment-id=\"46139\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Empat tampilan Indiana Jones di empat film bioskop. Sumber: LeCinedesFlemmards\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Empat tampilan Indiana Jones di empat film bioskop. Sumber: LeCinedesFlemmards&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46139\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian6.jpg\" alt=\"Empat tampilan Indiana Jones di empat film bioskop. Sumber: LeCinedesFlemmards\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46139\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Empat tampilan Indiana Jones di empat film bioskop. Sumber: LeCinedesFlemmards</p></div></p>\n<p>Mendiang River Phoenix berperan sebagai versi muda Indy (panggilan kecil Jones) di film <em>The Last Crusade</em> tahun 1989.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46136\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46136\" data-attachment-id=\"46136\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mendiang River Phoenix. Sumber: TheWrap\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mendiang River Phoenix. Sumber: TheWrap&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46136\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian3.jpg\" alt=\"Mendiang River Phoenix. Sumber: TheWrap\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46136\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mendiang River Phoenix. Sumber: TheWrap</p></div></p>\n<p>Corey Carrier memerankan Indy (usia 8–10 tahun) bersama Sean Patrick Flanery (usia 16–21) tahun dan George Hall (usia 93 tahun) di serial televisi “<em>The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles</em>” tahun 1992 – 1996.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46134\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46134\" data-attachment-id=\"46134\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Serial TV masa muda Indiana Jones. Sumber: Blu-ray\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Serial TV masa muda Indiana Jones. Sumber: Blu-ray&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46134\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian1.jpg\" alt=\"Serial TV masa muda Indiana Jones. Sumber: Blu-ray\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46134\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Serial TV masa muda Indiana Jones. Sumber: Blu-ray</p></div></p>\n<p>Selain penampilan yang khas, Indiana Jones juga dikenal dengan selera humor bagus, kecerdasan dan pemahaman tentang peradaban dan bahasa-bahasa kuno, serta phobia alias rasa takut yang besar pada ular.</p>\n<p><em>Franchise</em> ini awalnya diciptakan oleh George Lucas. Kenal dong, dengan George Lucas? Dia juga pencipta <em>franchise</em> laris lainnya seperti “Star Wars”. Saat berlibur ke Maui Hawaii, Lucas bertemu dengan rekannya sesama sineas film Steven Spielberg. Saat itu Spielberg mengatakan kalau dia ingin membuat film James Bond, dan Lucas mengatakan kalau dia “punya ide lebih bagus dari James Bond dan melibatkan Nazi”.</p>\n<p>Menggandeng Harrison Ford, yang berperan sebagai Han Solo di film George Lucas sebelumnya “Star Wars”, terjadilah film kolaborasi mereka yang diberi judul “<em>Raiders of the Lost Ark</em>”, yang menjadi pembuka lahirnya <em>franchise</em> baru “Indiana Jones”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46142\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46142\" data-attachment-id=\"46142\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian9/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian9.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Harrison Ford, Steven Spielberg &#038; George Lucas. Sumber: Pinterest\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Harrison Ford, Steven Spielberg &#038; George Lucas. Sumber: Pinterest&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian9-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian9.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46142\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian9.jpg\" alt=\"Harrison Ford, Steven Spielberg &amp; George Lucas. Sumber: Pinterest\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian9.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian9-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46142\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Harrison Ford, Steven Spielberg &amp; George Lucas. Sumber: Pinterest</p></div></p>\n<p>Berita terbarunya, karakter Indiana Jones yang sejak dulu merupakan seorang pria cerdas, macho, keren, manly, humoris serta<em> lovable</em> itu kini sedang dalam wacana untuk dirubah ke dalam format karakter wanita!</p>\n<p>Sutradara Steven Spielberg dalam wawancara dengan tabloid Inggris, The Sun, baru-baru ini mengonfirmasi kalau ada usulan untuk menjadikan Indiana Jones sebagai jagoan wanita.</p>\n<p>“Jika itu terjadi maka kita harus mengubah nama dia dari ‘Jones’ menjadi ‘Joan’. Dan tidak ada yang salah disitu” cetus Spielberg menanggapi usulan gender-swap Indiana Jones.</p>\n<p>Usulan tersebut muncul di tengah-tengah rencana pembuatan film kelima Indiana Jones yang direncanakan mulai syuting April 2019. Film itu juga dipastikan sebagai akhir Harrison Ford berperan sebagai Dr. Henry Walton Jones, Jr. alias Indiana Jones. Namun Spielberg memastikan kalau <em>franchise</em> ini akan terus berjalan selepas kepergian Harrison Ford.</p>\n<p>Dari kondisi itulah muncul usulan mengubah gender Indiana Jones; usulan yang hampir pasti berasal dari kelompok-kelompok feminist yang semakin sering mengutarakan perubahan-perubahan radikal pada <em>franchise</em> pop culture dunia yang sudah stabil.</p>\n<p>Belum diketahui reaksi George Lucas akan usulan ini, walaupun sebenarnya tidak akan banyak berpengaruh mengingat dia sudah menjual semua IP ciptaan dia ke Disney. Yang jelas, usulan menjadikan Indiana Jones menjadi karakter wanita itu oke, menurut Steven Spielberg. Tapi entah bagaimana menurut mayoritas fans? Karena ide gender-swap untuk <em>franchise</em> terkenal bisa jadi buruk saat di eksekusi.</p>\n<p><em>Case of point</em>: film all-females Ghostbusters terbaru. Yang ternyata tidak begitu laris di pasaran.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_46141\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-46141\" data-attachment-id=\"46141\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/menjadikan-indiana-jones-karakter-wanita-ide-buruk-atau-sebaliknya-steven-spielberg-tidak-keberatan/attachment/indian8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian8.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tidak se-sukses seperti harapan pihak studio. Sumber: IO9\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tidak se-sukses seperti harapan pihak studio. Sumber: IO9&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian8-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian8.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-46141\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian8.jpg\" alt=\"Tidak se-sukses seperti harapan pihak studio. Sumber: IO9\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian8.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/indian8-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-46141\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tidak se-sukses seperti harapan pihak studio. Sumber: IO9</p></div></p>\n<p>Baguskah mengubah Indiana Jones menjadi Indiana Joan? Menurut saya tidak. Tapi suarakan pendapat Anda sendiri! Bisa ditulis di kolom komentar di bawah.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"627af03c-d2e3-5f4e-81e4-96cfeef5fb6e"}}}